# F1Buddy – Budget Chatbot for International Students 🇺🇸🧳🍱

F1Buddy is a budget-friendly food and grocery chatbot tailored for international students in the U.S. It uses LLMs with live Yelp and Google Search APIs to help users find affordable restaurants and stores.

## 🚀 Features
- Find halal, vegetarian, Indian, or budget food near you
- Search groceries by cuisine or price
- Uses LLaMA3 (Groq) + Google Serper + Yelp
- Fast, interactive UI via Streamlit

## 🔧 Prerequisites
- Python 3.9+
- API keys for:
  - [Groq](https://console.groq.com/)
  - [Yelp](https://www.yelp.com/developers/v3/manage_app)
  - [Serper](https://serper.dev/)

## 🛠️ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/f1buddy-chatbot
cd f1buddy-chatbot
pip install -r requirements.txt
